Davido has just taken their relationship to another level. Sinzu who returned a few months ago from the US where he served a two-year jail sentence has just landed a major deal with DMW boss, Davido. The two have performed at Davido’s concert in DC. Davido has also vocal about his release showing that they have a strong relationship. The two have performed at Davido’s concert in DC and the two have teamed up on a hit track titled Carolina Guess we will be seeing more of the “Sinzu is Sinzu” game.